#. Tag: title
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Väljare"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following options apply to all &Qt; applications:"
msgstr "Följande väljare gäller alla program som använder &Qt;:"

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-style=</option> <replaceable>style</replaceable> / <option>-style</"
"option> <replaceable>style</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-style=</option> <replaceable>stil</replaceable> / <option>-style</"
"option> <replaceable>stil</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the application &GUI; style. Possible values depend on the system "
"configuration. If &Qt; is compiled with additional styles or has additional "
"styles as plugins these will be available to the <option>-style</option> "
"command line option."
msgstr ""
"Ställ in stilen för programmets grafiska användargränssnitt. Möjliga värden "
"beror på systeminställningen. Om &Qt; kompileras med ytterligare stilar "
"eller har ytterligare stilar som insticksmoduler är de tillgängliga för "
"kommandoradsväljaren <option>-style</option>."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-stylesheet=</option> <replaceable>stylesheet</replaceable> / "
"<option>-stylesheet</option> <replaceable>stylesheet</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-stylesheet=</option> <replaceable>stilmall</replaceable> / <option>-"
"stylesheet</option> <replaceable>stilmall</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the application styleSheet. The value must be a path to a file that "
"contains the Style Sheet."
msgstr ""
"Ställ in programmets stilmall. Värdet måste vara en sökväg till en fil som "
"innehåller stilmallen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "-widgetcount"
msgstr "-widgetcount"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Print debug message at the end about number of widgets left undestroyed and "
"maximum number of widgets existed at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Skriv ut felsökningsmeddelanden i slutet om antal oförstörda grafiska "
"komponenter som är kvar och maximalt antal grafiska komponenter som "
"existerade samtidigt."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "-reverse"
msgstr "-reverse"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the application's layout direction to <methodname>Qt::RightToLeft</"
"methodname>. This option is intended to aid debugging and should not be used "
"in production. The default value is automatically detected from the user's "
"locale (see also <methodname>QLocale::textDirection()</methodname>)."
msgstr ""
"Ställ in programmets layoutriktning till <methodname>Qt::RightToLeft</"
"methodname>. Alternativet är avsett att hjälpa till vid felsökning och ska "
"inte användas i produktion. Standardvärdet detekteras automatiskt från "
"användarens landsinställningar (se också <methodname>QLocale::"
"textDirection()</methodname>)."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qmljsdebugger=</option> <replaceable>port</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qmljsdebugger=</option> <replaceable>port</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activate the QML/JS debugger with a specified port. The value must be of "
"format port:1234[,block], where block is optional and will make the "
"application wait until a debugger connects to it."
msgstr ""
"Aktive QML/JS-avlusare med en angiven port. Värdet måste ha formatet "
"port:1234[,block], där block är valfritt och gör att programmet väntar till "
"avlusaren ansluter till den."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-platform</option> <replaceable>platformName[:options]</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-platform</option> <replaceable>plattformsnamn[:alternativ]</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the &Qt; Platform Abstraction (QPA) plugin."
msgstr "Ange insticksmodulen &Qt; Platform Abstraction (QPA)."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-platformpluginpath</option> <replaceable>path</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-platformpluginpath</option> <replaceable>sökväg</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the path to platform plugins."
msgstr "Ange sökvägen till plattformens insticksmoduler."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-platformtheme</option> <replaceable>platformTheme</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-platformtheme</option> <replaceable>plattformstema</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the platform theme."
msgstr "Ange plattformens tema."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-plugin</option> <replaceable>plugin</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-plugin</option> <replaceable>insticksmodul</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify additional plugins to load. The argument may appear multiple times."
msgstr ""
"Ange ytterligare insticksmoduler att ladda. Argumentet kan användas flera "
"gånger."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qwindowgeometry</option> <replaceable>geometry</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qwindowgeometry</option> <replaceable>geometri</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the window geometry for the main window using the &X11;-syntax. For "
"example: -qwindowgeometry 100x100+50+50"
msgstr ""
"Ange fönstergeometri för huvudfönstret med &X11;-syntax. Exempelvis: -"
"qwindowgeometry 100x100+50+50"

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qwindowicon</option> <replaceable>icon</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qwindowicon</option> <replaceable>ikon</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the default window icon."
msgstr "Ställ in förvald fönsterikon."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-qwindowtitle</option> <replaceable>title</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-qwindowtitle</option> <replaceable>namn</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the title of the first window."
msgstr "Ställ in det första fönstrets namn."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-session</option> <replaceable>session</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-session</option> <replaceable>session</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restore the application from an earlier session."
msgstr "Återställ programmet från en tidigare session."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-display</option> <replaceable>hostname:screen_number</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-display</option> <replaceable>värddatornamn:skärmnummer</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch displays on &X11;. Overrides the <envar>DISPLAY</envar> environment "
"variable."
msgstr "Byt skärm på &X11;. Överskrider miljövariabeln <envar>DISPLAY</envar>."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-geometry</option> <replaceable>geometry</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-geometry</option> <replaceable>geometri</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the window geometry for the main window on &X11;. For example: -"
"geometry 100x100+50+50"
msgstr ""
"Ange fönstergeometri för huvudfönstret på &X11;. Exempelvis: -geometry "
"100x100+50+50."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-dialogs=</option> <replaceable>[xp|none]</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-dialogs=</option> <replaceable>[xp|none]</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only available for the &Windows; platform. XP uses native style dialogs and "
"none disables them."
msgstr ""
"Bara tillgänglig för plattformen &Windows;. XP använder inbyggda dialogrutor "
"och none inaktiverar dem."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-fontengine=</option> <replaceable>freetype</replaceable>"
msgstr "<option>-fontengine=</option> <replaceable>freetype</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the FreeType font engine."
msgstr "Använd teckensnittsverktyget FreeType."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help and -? on &Windows;"
msgstr "-h, --help och -? på &Windows;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print all options and the application description."
msgstr "Skriv ut alla alternativ och programmets beskrivning."

#. Tag: option
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v --version"
msgstr "-v --version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the version string of the application."
msgstr "Visa programmets versionssträng."

#. Tag: title
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Se också"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<replaceable>kf6options</replaceable>(7)"
msgstr "<replaceable>kf6options</replaceable>(7)"

#. Tag: title
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "Upphovsmän"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Man page originally written by &Lauri.Watts; &Lauri.Watts.mail;"
msgstr "Manualsidan ursprungligen skriven av &Lauri.Watts; &Lauri.Watts.mail;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updated to &frameworks; 5 by &Burkhard.Lueck; &Burkhard.Lueck.mail;"
msgstr "Uppdaterad till Ramverk 5 av &Burkhard.Lueck; &Burkhard.Lueck.mail;"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The infos for this man page are from <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-6/"
"qapplication.html#QApplication\">QApplication documentation</ulink>, <ulink "
"url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-6/qguiapplication.html#QGuiApplication"
"\">QGuiApplication documentation</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/"
"qt-6/qcommandlineparser.html\">QCommandLineParser documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Informationen för den här manualsidan är från <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/"
"qt-6/qapplication.html#QApplication\">dokumentationen för QApplication</"
"ulink>, <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-6/qguiapplication."
"html#QGuiApplication\">dokumentationen för QGuiApplication</ulink> och "
"<ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-6/qcommandlineparser.html"
"\">dokumentationen för QCommandLineParser</ulink>."

#~ msgid "Qt 5.4"
#~ msgstr "Qt 5.4"

#~ msgid "qt5options User's Manual"
#~ msgstr "qt5options användarhandbok"

#~ msgid "><option>-v --version</option>"
#~ msgstr "<option>-v --version</option>"

#~ msgid "2014-03-04"
#~ msgstr "2014-03-04"

#~ msgid "Frameworks 5.0"
#~ msgstr "Ramverk 5.0"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<command><replaceable>Qt application</replaceable></command> <arg choice="
#~ "\"opt\">Qt Generic Options</arg>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<command><replaceable>QT-program</replaceable></command> <arg choice=\"opt"
#~ "\">Allmänna QT-väljare</arg>"

#~ msgid "<option>--display</option> <parameter>displayname</parameter>"
#~ msgstr "<option>--display</option> <parameter>skärmnamn</parameter>"

#~ msgid "Use the X-server display <parameter>displayname</parameter>."
#~ msgstr "Använd X-serverskärmen <parameter>skärmnamn</parameter>."

#~ msgid "<option>--session</option> <parameter>sessionId</parameter>"
#~ msgstr "<option>--session</option> <parameter>sessions-id</parameter>"

#~ msgid "--cmap"
#~ msgstr "--cmap"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Causes the application to install a private color map on an 8-bit display."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Gör att programmet installerar en privat färgkarta på en 8-bitarsskärm."

#~ msgid "<option>--ncols</option> <parameter>count</parameter>"
#~ msgstr "<option>--ncols</option> <parameter>antal</parameter>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Limits the number of colors allocated in the color cube on an 8-bit "
#~ "display, if the application is using the <methodname>QApplication::"
#~ "ManyColor</methodname> color specification."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Begränsar antal färger som tilldelas i färgkuben för en 8-bitars skärm, "
#~ "om programmet använder färgspecifikationen <methodname>QApplication::"
#~ "ManyColor</methodname>."

#~ msgid "--nograb"
#~ msgstr "--nograb"

#~ msgid "Tells &Qt; to never grab the mouse or the keyboard."
#~ msgstr "Talar om för &Qt; att aldrig låsa musen eller tangentbordet."

#~ msgid "--dograb"
#~ msgstr "--dograb"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Running under a debugger can cause an implicit <option>--nograb</option>, "
#~ "use <option>--dograb</option> to override."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Att köra med en avlusare kan orsaka en implicit <option>--nograb</"
#~ "option>. Använd <option>--dograb</option> för att överskrida det."

#~ msgid "--sync"
#~ msgstr "--sync"

#~ msgid "Switches to synchronous mode for debugging."
#~ msgstr "Byter till synkront läge för avlusning."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<option>--fn</option>,<option>--font</option> <parameter>fontname</"
#~ "parameter>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<option>--fn</option>,<option>--font</option> <parameter>teckensnitt</"
#~ "parameter>"

#~ msgid "Defines the application font."
#~ msgstr "Definierar programmets teckensnitt."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<option>--bg</option>,<option>--background</option> <parameter>color</"
#~ "parameter>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<option>--bg</option>,<option>--background</option> <parameter>färg</"
#~ "parameter>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Sets the default background color and an application palette (light and "
#~ "dark shades are calculated)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ställer in förvald bakgrundsfärg och en programpalett (ljusa och mörka "
#~ "nyanser beräknas)."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<option>--fg</option>,<option>--foreground</option> <parameter>color</"
#~ "parameter>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<option>--fg</option>,<option>--foreground</option> <parameter>färg</"
#~ "parameter>"

#~ msgid "Sets the default foreground color"
#~ msgstr "Ställer in förvald förgrundsfärg"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<option>--btn</option>,<option>--button</option> <parameter>color</"
#~ "parameter>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<option>--btn</option>,<option>--button</option> <parameter>färg</"
#~ "parameter>"

#~ msgid "<option>--name</option> <parameter>name</parameter>"
#~ msgstr "<option>--name</option> <parameter>namn</parameter>"

#~ msgid "<option>--title</option> <parameter>title</parameter>"
#~ msgstr "<option>--title</option> <parameter>titel</parameter>"

#~ msgid "<option>--visual</option> <parameter>TrueColor</parameter>"
#~ msgstr "<option>--visual</option> <parameter>TrueColor</parameter>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Forces the application to use a <parameter>TrueColor</parameter> visual "
#~ "on an 8-bit display."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Tvingar programmet att använda <parameter>TrueColor</parameter> med en 8-"
#~ "bitars skärm."

#~ msgid "<option>--inputstyle</option> <parameter>inputstyle</parameter>"
#~ msgstr "<option>--inputstyle</option> <parameter>inmatningsstil</parameter>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Sets XIM (X Input Method) input style. Possible values are "
#~ "<parameter>onthespot</parameter>, <parameter>overthespot</parameter>, "
